headline: 3 Reasons to Sell DE and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Since June 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 97.7%. But one standout stock has more than doubled the market - over the past five years, Deere has surged 236% to $520.65 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 18.5% in the last six months thanks to its solid quarterly results, beating the S&P by 19%.
